'''Luiz Carlos de Souza Pinto Junior''' or just '''Luiz Carlos''' (born [[31 August]] [[1980]]) is a [[Brazil]]ian professional [[Football (soccer)|football]] forward. He is currently [[free agent|unattached]].

Luiz Carlos most recently played for [[Danish Superliga]] side [[Viborg FF]].

